{"tid":2055744,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁君彥指示秘書處徹底清潔議員貯物櫃　日後不能上鎖","createTime":"2020-06-08T07:50:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T08:54:33.000Z","uid":60281,"like":4,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"162bbad484879e16ca7c6991d47ebcefabba1860","tid":2055744,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T07:50:31.000Z","msg":"立法會決定，議員於會議廳內的貯物櫃不准上鎖。<br />\n<br />\n立法會秘書處指，按立法會行管會主席梁君彥指示，將徹底清潔及檢查立法會會議廳，包括議員座位的貯物櫃，並要求議員明天上午10時至12時期間，移走議員貯物櫃內物品，日後貯物櫃亦不能再上鎖，並交由秘書處清潔及檢查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530833-20200608.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530833-20200608.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=jILigwfPQQ17AL812Qo3KTBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=7a9e0a3c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530833-20200608.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=89f4d522\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530833-20200608.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"c642eda831f046f8c9f3948ed7916494ab392724","tid":2055744,"uid":132587,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T07:52:11.000Z","msg":"唔鎖得咁同擺d野落你個口度有咩分別"},{"pid":"7409db6145527581b44886c42768d574ef8acd95","tid":2055744,"uid":183844,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T07:53:15.000Z","msg":"cls<br />\n當自己皇帝呀"},{"pid":"c43f96bfe1717c9897e03478531aa7a55ff1e5c9","tid":2055744,"uid":204539,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T07:56:00.000Z","msg":"*此安排只適用於非獻世派議員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d201e7fd5fdebc218f833002df182fb699872ed1","tid":2055744,"uid":72994,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T07:56:32.000Z","msg":"諗起中學查locker啲fd要拎走啲輕小說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac